### 1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY
In accordance with the CARSS Wave 7 Runtime Alignment Program and the Wave 5 Schema Registry, runtime authority for point-of-sale journal records has been successfully transferred from the legacy `pos_transactions` table to the certified constitutional `transactions` table. All codebases are compiling successfully, and zero legacy tables are written to.

